### Notification Integration

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **Name** | `{{ prefix }}_NOTIFY_EMAIL` |
| **Type** | Email |
| **Recipient** | `{{ notification_email }}` |

### Alert Configuration

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **Alert Name** | `RESOURCE_MONITOR_ALERT` |
| **Location** | `{{ prefix }}_{{ data_zones[0].name | upper }}.ALERTS` |
| **Schedule** | Every hour |
| **Warehouse** | `{{ prefix }}_WH_{{ warehouse_configuration[0].name | upper }}` |
| **Condition** | Resource monitor >= 75% usage |

### Alert Triggers

When the resource monitor crosses these thresholds, you'll receive notifications:

| Threshold | Action | Via |
|-----------|--------|-----|
| 50% | Notify | Built-in (account admins) |
| 75% | Notify | Built-in + Custom alert |
| 90% | Notify | Built-in (account admins) |
| 100% | Suspend | Warehouses suspended |

{%- else %}

### No Notification Email Configured

To enable notifications, provide an email address in the `notification_email` answer.

**Alternative Notifications:**
1. **Snowsight Notifications**: Configure in Admin → Notifications
2. **Built-in Monitor Notifications**: Sent to account admins automatically
3. **Third-party Integration**: Use webhooks or message queues

{%- endif %}

